you're going to record.

04:19.358 --> 04:20.825
Okay.

04:20.827 --> 04:22.893
Okay.

04:28.900 --> 04:30.868
Hello. My name is James,

04:30.870 --> 04:35.039
and this little guy
is 150 milligrams

04:35.041 --> 04:38.743
of specially enhanced
Dimethyltryptamine, DMT 19.

04:38.745 --> 04:42.747
It's supposedly impossible
to find, but here I have it.

04:42.749 --> 04:47.084
Well, where'd you get it?
Some friends in Colorado.

04:59.364 --> 05:01.799
Oh, uh, FYI, Renny,

05:01.801 --> 05:06.470
