YouTube.

05:45.378 --> 05:47.244
Well, if you do anything
remotely funny,

05:47.246 --> 05:48.546
I might actually save it.

05:48.548 --> 05:50.681
Don't fuck with me, Renny.

05:54.052 --> 05:55.486
So if nothing happens,

05:55.488 --> 05:58.522
are you gonna just make
something up for your book?

06:03.196 --> 06:05.863
Wait. Do you...

06:05.865 --> 06:08.332
What is that?

06:08.334 --> 06:10.568
Do you hear that?

06:10.570 --> 06:12.903
That radio?

06:16.876 --> 06:18.976
Where's it coming from?

06:18.978 --> 06:21.145
It's like interference.

06:56.015 --> 06:57.281
What is that?

06:57.283 --> 06:58.482
Wait.

07:04.156 --> 07:07.958
What if it's coming from
something in the house?

07:28.647 --> 07:30.815
Do you think someone's here?

07:45.263 --> 07:47.465
I don't like this.
We should call someone.

07:47.467 --> 07:49.066
I ingested the chemical, remember?

07:49.068 --> 07:50.434
I took that. We don't...

07:51.571 --> 07:53.471
Oh, fuck, Renny.

07:53.473 --> 07:54.705
What?

07:54.707 --> 07:57.508
It's coming towards the house.

07:57.510 --> 08:01.111
What is?
I don't know.

08:08.753 --> 08:10.721
What is this?!

08:12.224 --> 08:14.058
What do you want me to do?

08:14.060 --> 08:16.861
This...

08:16.863 --> 08:18.262
Help!

08:48.493 --> 08:51.028
Look, you think maybe he
was having some kind of spasm,

08:51.030 --> 08:53.097
