08:54.700 --> 08:56.166
Can you recall making any movements

08:56.168 --> 08:58.135
to strike or push him
when he was convulsing?

08:58.137 --> 08:59.303
Is that how it happened?

08:59.305 --> 09:02.506
No, I...
No. I just ran.

09:02.508 --> 09:04.875
I don't know what happened...
And you didn't take the drug?

09:04.877 --> 09:06.477
No, I didn't.
Are you sure?

09:06.479 --> 09:08.178
I didn't take the chemical!

09:09.714 --> 09:12.349
James and I didn't see
each other much after college.

09:12.351 --> 09:13.751
True to both our words,

09:13.753 --> 09:16.086
he struggled as a young,
but talented novelist.

09:16.088 --> 09:18.856
I got into journalism
at an online news site.

09:18.858 --> 09:21.559
Occasionally, we'd drop
each other an email

09:21.561 --> 09:24.161
just to check in.

09:24.163 --> 09:26.797
No one could tell me exactly
what had happened to James

09:26.799 --> 09:28.966
because no one knew.

09:28.968 --> 09:31.235
Nevada law enforcement
officials suspected

09:31.237 --> 09:33.971
he'd been murdered
by his friend, Renny Seegan,

09:33.973 --> 09:36.073
after James ingested
an enhanced form

09:36.075 --> 09:40.911
of a rare contraband chemical
known as Dimethyltryptamine.

09:40.913 --> 09:42.413
I been real nice up to now,

09:42.415 --> 09:44.615
but I'm gonna...
I'm gonna fuck your world, kid.

09:44.617 --> 09:45.816
Have you seen the kind of boys

09:45.818 --> 09:47.351
we got down there
in the county lockup?

09:47.353 --> 09:48.852
I'm gonna put you in there
with those son of a bitches.

09:48.854 --> 09:50.788
I didn't do...
I didn't do anything.

09:50.790 --> 09:52.890
Fresh piece of fucking chicken!

09:52.892 --> 09:57.061
All I know is he said it was
from some friends in Colorado.

09:57.063 --> 09:58.162
God.

09:58.164 --> 09:59.530
Oh, yeah.

09:59.532 --> 10:01.131
I hear that every time... friends.

10:01.133 --> 10:03.033
What kind of friend
gives you poison?

10:03.035 --> 10:05.269
Without a body,
police weren't ready

10:05.271 --> 10:07.771
to charge Renny Seegan
with any crime.

10:07.773 --> 10:10.107
They would never get the chance.

10:10.109 --> 10:12.776
Renny vanished
almost 72 hours later.

10:12.778 --> 10:15.179
He was never seen again.

10:17.882 --> 10:19.850
I decided that James
and I would work

10:19.852 --> 10:21.986
on one last project together.

10:21.988 --> 10:25.756
We would find out the truth
about what happened to him.

10:25.758 --> 10:28.392
It would be our final collaboration.

