middle of nowhere,

18:14.560 --> 18:18.128
75 miles from the nearest town,

18:18.130 --> 18:21.264
on the outskirts of the
Black Rock Desert...

18:23.702 --> 18:28.538
Listening, watching
for the Lonely Traveler.

18:28.540 --> 18:30.407
Happy times.

18:53.164 --> 18:55.332
<i>♪ Don't know where</i>

18:56.300 --> 18:58.401
James was more than a friend.

19:02.774 --> 19:06.443
